-- Swiss Economy Minister Criticizes Franc Discussions, AWP Reports
-- B y   E l e n a   L o g u t e n k o v a
-- 2012-06-13T05:59:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-13/swiss-economy-minister-criticizes-franc-discussions-awp-reports.html
Swiss Economy Minister Johann Schneider-Ammann criticized public discussions about the Swiss
central bank’s franc ceiling of 1.20 versus the euro, AWP
newswire reported, citing his remarks at Club Suisse de la
Presse in Geneva yesterday.  The  Swiss National Bank ’s franc ceiling is “absolutely
necessary” to defend the country’s economy, he said, according
to AWP.  To contact the reporter on this story:
